<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1) Ni ma na yi zunubai fa
 Dukakanmu, mun yi zunubi
 Muka kasa daraja ta Allah.

[V2]
 2) Yesu Kristi ne Mai Ceto
 Shi ne Macecinmu duka.
 Shi ya mutu domin zunubanmu.

[V3]
 3) Ni na faɗi laifofina,
 Kai ka faɗi laifofinka
 Don ka sami gafara da tsira.

[V4]
 4) Mutane ko kun yi shiri ?
 Yesu Kristi shina zuwa
 Don shi karɓi masu bangaskiya.</lyrics>
<title>Ni Ma Na Yi Zunubai Fa LW497</title>
<hymn_number>497</hymn_number>
</song>